  }, "Personality Quirks:"), " Loving and maternal demeanor, but always has a quick, biting comeback to any sign of disrespect. Offers counterintuitive wisdom. Basically, she\u2019s like the Oracle from the Matrix, with the suppressed anger of Anakin Skywalker.\nAppearance: African-American woman with white hair. She has a clearly visible scar on the side of her forehead. She dresses professionally, but also wears large, flashy, African bangles and necklaces.\n", mdx("strong", {
