ns"), mdx("p", null, "When playing mini-games with native speakers of the target language, players must wait in the Native Queue until a Native Speaker is available. These purchasable tokens will allow players to skip instantly to the front of the queue, bypassing the wait."), mdx("br", null), mdx("h1", null, "APPENDIX 1: Example Can-Do Statements"), mdx("p", null, "Interpersonal Communication"), mdx("h2", null, "Interpersonal Communication Levels"), mdx("h3", null, "Novice Low"), mdx("p", null, "I can communicate on some very familiar topics using single words and phrases that I have practiced and memorized."), mdx("h3", null, "Novice Mid"), mdx("p", null, "I can communicate on very familiar topics using a variety of words and phrases that I have practiced and memorized."), mdx("h3", null, "Novice High"), mdx("p", null, "I can communicate and exchange information about familiar topics using phrases and simple sentences, sometimes supported by memorized language. I can usually handle short social interactions in everyday situations by asking and answering simple questions."), mdx("h3", null, "Intermediate Low"), mdx("p", null, "I can participate in conversations on a number of familiar topics using simple sentences. I can handle short social interactions in everyday situations by asking and answering simple questions."), mdx("h3", null, "Intermediate Mid"), mdx("p", null, "I can participate in conversations on familiar topics using sentences and series of sentences. I can handle short social interactions in everyday situations by asking and answering a variety of questions. I can usually say what I want to say about myself and my everyday life."), mdx("h3", null, "Intermediate High"), mdx("p", null, "I can participate with ease and confidence in conversations on familiar topics. I can usually talk about events and experiences in various time frames. I can usually describe people, places, and things. I can handle social interactions in everyday situations, sometimes 